org.jamesframework.core.subset.validations

Class SubsetValidation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamesframework.core.subset.validations.SubsetValidation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validation

    public class SubsetValidation
extends Object
implements Validation
    Represents a validation of a subset solution. Separately indicates whether the subset has a valid size, in addition to the general mandatory constraint validation. It can be checked whether the subset passed validation, possibly ignoring its size.
    Author:
    Herman De Beukelaer
